CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, January 20, 1962, pg. A13 reads:" Leaving Church - Mr. and Mrs. Russell D. Jackson Jr. smile happily as they leave St. James AME Church, following their recent wedding. The bride is the former LaVerne C. Edwards, daughter of Mr. and Mrs. Harry S. Edwards. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Groom Russell D. Jackson Jr. and bride LaVerne C. Edwards Jackson posed in front of car
